    {
      "sectionType": "text",
      "text": "Below is a NextJS announcement slider component for the new <a href='https://chalkfestival.org' target='_blank'>Chalk Festival</a> website that I am designing (<a href='/examples/chalkfestival' target='_blank'>see preview</a>) and building. It utilizes the <b>jotai</b> state management library to manage app states. The slider allows navigation between announcements through buttons. The data is fetched asynchronously using the <b>fetchData</b> utility from the Sanity.io client. The component dynamically renders announcements based on fetched data, and each announcement may include an optional link."
